<div><b><span style="font-size: 12pt">向自由想象致敬！<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></div>
<div style="text-indent: 24pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt">小米2013年春季校园招聘</span></b></div>
<div style="line-height: 18pt; background: white">抢票抢号抢手机，不如抢小米春招岗位！</div>
<div style="line-height: 18pt; background: white">技术类、编辑类等诸多岗位等你来挑战！</div>
<div style="line-height: 18pt; background: white">创新、快速的文化和平等的伙伴式氛围给你无限自由！</div>
<div style="line-height: 18pt; background: white">加入小米，让想象飞一会儿！</div>
<div align="center"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>
<div><b><span style="font-size: 14pt">2013</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 14pt">春季校招流程：</span></b></div>
<div>简历投递&rarr;笔试通知&rarr;面试通知&rarr;<span>offer</span></div>
<div><span style="color: red">简历投递邮箱：</span><span style="color: red"><a href="mailto:campus@xiaomi.com"><span style="color: red">campus@xiaomi.com</span></a></span></div>
